snippet.title: TIME BREAKER Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
TIME BREAKER is a single player, first person puzzle game mixing puzzle and storyline, created by one-person. You play as Judy, she wakes up in a strange facility called « Naera Laboratory ». Everyone is dead, but someone seems to be alive, it’s « Anna » the last scientist alive.

TIME BREAKER Gameplay Trailer
